The life of Satou Kazuma, a hikikomori who likes games, all too soon came to an end because of a traffic accident... It was supposed to, but when he woke up, a beautiful girl who called herself a goddess was in front of his eyes. \"Hey, I have got something a little nice for you. Wanna go to another world? You can take only one thing of your choice along with you.\" \"...then I'll take you.\" From here on, the great adventure of subjugating the Demon King will begin for the reincarnated Kazuma... Or so one would think, but it's the labor for obtaining food, clothing and shelter that begins! Despite Kazuma wanting to live in peace, the goddess keeps causing problems one after another, and eventually, they attract the attention of the Demon King's army!?

Gamer Kazuma dies in a freak accident, and is met in the afterlife by a crass goddess, Aqua.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/545681"}}},{"id":550442,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/550442/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x02-an-explosion-for-this-chuunibyou","name":"An Explosion For This Chuunibyou!","season":1,"number":2,"airdate":"2016-01-20","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-01-20T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209265.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209265.jpg"},"summary":"

It's great for Kazuma that he brought Aqua along with him, but unlike in a game world, much is missing from his adventurer's lifestyle. No money, no equipment, and even fighting the lowest ranking monsters is a hard-fought battle. That's when they decide to recruit new party members.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/550442"}}},{"id":550443,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/550443/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x03-a-panty-treasure-in-this-right-hand","name":"A Panty Treasure In This Right Hand!","season":1,"number":3,"airdate":"2016-01-27","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-01-27T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209261.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209261.jpg"},"summary":"

A low-grade goddess turned arch priest who works hard to acquire party trick skills, a disappointing arch wizard who can only unleash explosion magic once per day, and Kazuma himself, whose only redeeming quality is his good luck. Kazuma despairs over the completely useless party that's been formed.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/550443"}}},{"id":550444,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/550444/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x04-explosion-magic-for-this-formidable-enemy","name":"Explosion Magic for This Formidable Enemy!","season":1,"number":4,"airdate":"2016-02-03","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-02-03T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209262.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209262.jpg"},"summary":"

All of the weak monsters have gone into hiding since a leader of the devil king's army has settled in near town. Kazuma, who had been focusing on improving his skills, is stuck at a standstill. With nothing else to do, Kazuma tags along with Megumin's training, which consists of unleashing explosion magic into an abandoned castle.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/550444"}}},{"id":550445,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/550445/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x05-a-price-for-this-cursed-sword","name":"A Price For This Cursed Sword!","season":1,"number":5,"airdate":"2016-02-10","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-02-10T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209263.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209263.jpg"},"summary":"

Wanting to earn some money despite only hard quests being available, Aqua takes on a request to purify a lake filled with alligator monsters, with the others putting her in a cage to keep her safe.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/550445"}}},{"id":560440,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/560440/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x06-a-conclusion-to-this-worthless-fight","name":"A Conclusion to This Worthless Fight!","season":1,"number":6,"airdate":"2016-02-17","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-02-17T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209264.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209264.jpg"},"summary":"

Annoyed that Megumin had still been using his castle for explosion practice, Verdia, after proving easily susceptible to Aqua's purification magic, summons an undead army which is quickly defeated by Megumin's explosion magic.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/560440"}}},{"id":569184,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/569184/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x07-a-second-death-in-this-freezing-season","name":"A Second Death in This Freezing Season!","season":1,"number":7,"airdate":"2016-02-24","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-02-24T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209267.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209267.jpg"},"summary":"

Needing money to pay off his debts despite the freezing weather, Kazuma and his party takes on a quest to kill Snow Sprites.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/569184"}}},{"id":569185,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/569185/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x08-a-loving-hand-for-our-party-when-we-cant-make-it-through-winter","name":"A Loving Hand For Our Party When We Can't Make It Through Winter!","season":1,"number":8,"airdate":"2016-03-02","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-03-02T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209268.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209268.jpg"},"summary":"

Kazuma and Aqua visit a magic shop run by a kind-hearted lich named Wiz, who reveals herself to be one of the Devil King's generals in charge of protecting a barrier surrounding the Devil King's castle.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/569185"}}},{"id":569186,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/569186/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x09-gods-blessing-on-this-wonderful-shop","name":"God's Blessing on This Wonderful Shop!","season":1,"number":9,"airdate":"2016-03-09","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-03-09T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209269.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209269.jpg"},"summary":"

Kazuma and his adventure friends Keith and Dust go to a shop run by succubi who provide male adventurers with much needed relief by giving them erotic dreams.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/569186"}}},{"id":569187,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/569187/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-1x10-a-final-flame-for-this-over-the-top-fortress","name":"A Final Flame for this Over-the-top Fortress!","season":1,"number":10,"airdate":"2016-03-16","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2016-03-16T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209270.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/83/209270.jpg"},"summary":"

With their members being perfectly suited for the job, Kazuma's party, along with Wiz, are chosen to lead an attack against the Destroyer.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/569187"}}},{"id":972360,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/972360/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x01-give-me-deliverance-from-this-judicial-injustice","name":"Give Me Deliverance from this Judicial Injustice!","season":2,"number":1,"airdate":"2017-01-11","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-01-11T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/92/232418.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/92/232418.jpg"},"summary":"

Finding no support from his allies, Kazuma is arrested for treason due to accidentally blowing up a noble's mansion.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/972360"}}},{"id":1030214,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030214/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x02-a-friend-for-this-crimson-demon-girl","name":"A Friend for This Crimson Demon Girl!","season":2,"number":2,"airdate":"2017-01-18","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-01-18T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/95/238844.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/95/238844.jpg"},"summary":"

As Kazuma notices that Darkness hasn't come back since negotiating with Alderp, Megumin brings in a cat that she names Chomusuke.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030214"}}},{"id":1030215,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030215/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x03-peace-for-the-master-of-this-labyrinth","name":"Peace for the Master of This Labyrinth!","season":2,"number":3,"airdate":"2017-01-25","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-01-25T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/95/238845.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/95/238845.jpg"},"summary":"

Wanting to earn some real money, Kazuma and Aqua go to explore a newly discovered pathway in Keele's Dungeon, coming across gremlins, mimics, and the undead along the way.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030215"}}},{"id":1030216,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030216/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x04-a-betrothed-for-this-noble-daughter","name":"A Betrothed for This Noble Daughter!","season":2,"number":4,"airdate":"2017-02-01","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-02-01T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/96/240233.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/96/240233.jpg"},"summary":"

Darkness suddenly returns, asking for the others' help in getting out of an arranged marriage with the Alderp's son, Walther.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030216"}}},{"id":1030549,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030549/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x05-servitude-for-this-masked-knight","name":"Servitude for This Masked Knight!","season":2,"number":5,"airdate":"2017-02-08","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-02-08T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/97/243299.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/97/243299.jpg"},"summary":"

As a result of a magic circle that Aqua had drawn in Keele's dungeon, strange explosive doll monsters have started to appear, putting the town at risk.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030549"}}},{"id":1030550,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030550/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x06-goodbye-to-this-irritating-living-world","name":"Goodbye to This Irritating Living World!","season":2,"number":6,"airdate":"2017-02-15","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-02-15T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/98/246504.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/98/246504.jpg"},"summary":"

Kazuma is surprised to discover that Vanir had an extra life and has since quit his position as a commander to work at Wiz's shop, striking up a business partnership to sell products from Kazuma's world.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030550"}}},{"id":1030551,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030551/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x07-an-invitation-for-this-knucklehead","name":"An Invitation for This Knucklehead!","season":2,"number":7,"airdate":"2017-02-22","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-02-22T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/99/249079.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/99/249079.jpg"},"summary":"

Vanir gives Kazuma the choice of either selling the intellectual rights for his real world products for a one-off payment of 300 million eris, or maintaining a profit-sharing contract of 1 million eris a month.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030551"}}},{"id":1030552,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030552/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x08-sightseeing-in-this-pitiful-city","name":"Sightseeing in This Pitiful City!","season":2,"number":8,"airdate":"2017-03-01","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-03-01T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/100/250975.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/100/250975.jpg"},"summary":"

Kazuma and the others manage to lure the kite hawks into a cave and deal with them all at once, only to cause more trouble for the other travellers later when Aqua attracts some zombies.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030552"}}},{"id":1087319,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1087319/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x09-a-goddess-for-this-corrupt-hot-springs-town","name":"A Goddess for This Corrupt Hot Springs Town!","season":2,"number":9,"airdate":"2017-03-08","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-03-08T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/101/253564.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/101/253564.jpg"},"summary":"

After witnessing Aqua warp the town's citizens with her petty confessional hearings, Kazuma takes a dip in the mixed bath, where he comes across another man who is as sick of the town's behavior as he is.

","_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1087319"}}},{"id":1030554,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1030554/kono-subarashii-sekai-ni-shukufuku-o-2x10-gods-blessing-on-this-wonderful-party","name":"God's Blessing on This Wonderful Party!","season":2,"number":10,"airdate":"2017-03-15","airtime":"01:05","airstamp":"2017-03-15T16:05:00+00:00","runtime":25,"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/102/255658.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/102/255658.jpg"},"summary":"

Evading the angry mob, the gang discover that the source of the town's water is being poisoned by the man from earlier, who is revealed to be one of the Devil King's army leaders, Hans the Deadly Poison Slime.
